{"analytics_identifier":"PB1327","base_path":"/government/organisations/trade-remedies-authority","content_id":"649fc487-7d9d-4c44-828e-bfb5abea94f7","description":"The Trade Remedies Authority exists to defend the UK against unfair international trade practices. We investigate whether new trade remedies are needed to prevent injury to UK industries caused by unfair trading practices and make recommendations on appropriate measures to defend UK economic interests. Trade Remedies Authority is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Business and Trade .","details":{"acronym":"","alternative_format_contact_email":"contact@traderemedies.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Trade Remedies Authority exists to defend the UK against unfair international trade practices. We investigate whether new trade remedies are needed to prevent injury to UK industries caused by unfair trading practices and make recommendations on appropriate measures to defend UK economic interests.</p>\n\n<p>Trade Remedies Authority is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/department-for-business-and-trade\">Department for Business and Trade</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"department-for-business-trade","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67a9ef0731fb10faa3148476/s960_Untitled_design__20_.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67a9ef0731fb10faa3148474/s300_Untitled_design__20_.png"},"foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"dbt","formatted_title":"Trade Remedies Authority"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/trade-remedies-authority/about/complaints-procedure","title":"Complaints procedure"},{"href":"/government/organisations/trade-remedies-authority/about/media-enquiries","title":"Media enquiries"},{"href":"/government/organisations/trade-remedies-authority/about/our-governance","title":"Our governance"},{"href":"/government/organisations/trade-remedies-authority/about/recruitment","title":"Working for Trade Remedies Authority"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/defending-uk-trade-with-greater-pace-and-purpose","image":{"alt_text":"Cover graphic titled “Defending UK trade with greater pace and purpose – The TRA Plan 2026 to 2029","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69f3523a5c1bc131b7d1eb99/s712_TRA_Plan_GOV.UK.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69f3523aab602a88957eef46/s465_TRA_Plan_GOV.UK.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69f3523a5c1bc131b7d1eb98/TRA_Plan_GOV.UK.png"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-30T13:53:31.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>TRA sets out three-year plan to defend UK businesses from unfair trade.</p>\n</div>","title":"Defending UK trade with greater pace and purpose"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/welded-tubes-and-pipes-expiry-review-reaches-initial-findings","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69ef7abf20a498c16734b014/s712_Copy_of_Biodiesel_Idonesia_option_2_.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69ef7abfd36883a64473ba40/s465_Copy_of_Biodiesel_Idonesia_option_2_.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69ef7abf20a498c16734b015/Copy_of_Biodiesel_Idonesia_option_2_.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-27T16:02:31.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The TRA has initially proposed that an anti-dumping measure on welded tubes and pipes from Belarus and China be extended at unchanged rates.</p>\n</div>","title":"Welded tubes and pipes expiry review reaches initial findings"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/tra-proposes-new-measure-on-south-korean-hot-rolled-steel-plate","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69ea2a2d08ecdb5c6f34aee1/s712_Copy_of_Biodiesel_Idonesia_option_2___2_.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69ea2a2dd36883a64473b8f2/s465_Copy_of_Biodiesel_Idonesia_option_2___2_.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69ea2a2dd36883a64473b8f3/Copy_of_Biodiesel_Idonesia_option_2___2_.png"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-23T15:13:50.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The TRA has proposed a new anti-dumping measure be imposed on imports of hot rolled steel plate from South Korea.</p>\n\n</div>","title":"TRA proposes new measure on South Korean hot rolled steel plate"},{"document_type":"Research","href":"/government/publications/import-trends-monitor","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/693a90a26a12691d48491dcb/s712_Strategic_steer_news_story.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/693a90a2cfacd5e888491dc7/s465_Strategic_steer_news_story.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/693a90a2cfacd5e888491dc6/Strategic_steer_news_story.png"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-28T11:10:42.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>This new tool provides import data for goods to the UK over the past year, helping identify anomalies in volume and prices that may affect UK producers.</p>\n</div>","title":"UK Import Trends Monitor"},{"document_type":"Guidance","href":"/government/publications/the-uk-trade-remedies-system-practical-guides-for-small-and-medium-sized-businesses-smes","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67a4ec444dd52dddeb16a869/s712_SME_Handbook_Update.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67a4ec44a9f973ede06b3c82/s465_SME_Handbook_Update.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67a4ec440e720adbd4f6ae15/SME_Handbook_Update.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2024-05-09T14:18:06.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>A handbook for small and medium-sized businesses (SMEs) interested in the UK trade remedies system and working with the Trade Remedies Authority (TRA).</p>\n</div>","title":"The UK trade remedies system – practical guides for businesses"},{"document_type":"Guidance","href":"/government/publications/the-uk-trade-remedies-investigations-process","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/679b477615f01fdf8e05e760/s712_Investigation_process_graphic.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/679b4776413ef177de146be0/s465_Investigation_process_graphic.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/679b4776abe77b74cc146be2/Investigation_process_graphic.png"},"public_updated_at":"2025-11-05T12:09:07.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>How the UK’s Trade Remedies Authority investigates whether trade remedy measures are needed to counteract unfair import practices.</p>\n</div>","title":"The UK trade remedies investigations process"}],"ordered_featured_links":[{"href":"https://www.trade-remedies.service.gov.uk/accounts/login/","title":"Sign in to the Trade Remedies Service or apply for an investigation"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/trade-remedies-authority#org-contacts","title":"Contact the Trade Remedies Authority"},{"href":"https://www.trade-remedies.service.gov.uk/public/cases/","title":"Find out about live and completed cases"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/the-uk-trade-remedies-investigations-process","title":"View trade remedies guidance"}],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"service","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"executive_ndpb","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"