rvice.gov.uk/media/5a4f673aed915d5954733c16/s465_nick_baird.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"ae47614f-d738-4aaf-8fc7-93fe2f8c01e7","details":{"current":false,"ended_on":"2013-12-13T00:00:00+00:00","person_appointment_order":1,"started_on":"2011-09-01T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"84614171-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Chief Executive of UK Trade and Investment (<abbr title=\"UK Trade and Investment\">UKTI</abbr>) was accountable for developing and implementing exports and inward investment strategy on behalf of Her Majesty’s Government (<abbr title=\"Her Majesty's Government\">HMG</abbr>).</p>\n\n<p>The Chief Executive:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>provided clear leadership to <abbr title=\"UK Trade and Investment\">UKTI</abbr> and across Whitehall to help <abbr title=\"Her Majesty's Government\">HMG</abbr> meet the challenges and opportunities for UK exports and inward investment</li>\n  <li>chaired the senior cross-Whitehall Exports and Investment Board on behalf of the Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills (<abbr title=\"Department for Business, Innovation and Skills\">BIS</abbr>)</li>\n  <li>directly advised the Ministerial Exports Implementation Task Force</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The Chief Executive sat on the <abbr title=\"Department for Business, Innovation and Skills\">BIS</abbr> Executive and Departmental Boards, and the Foreign and Commonwealth Office (<abbr title=\"Foreign and Commonwealth Office\">FCO</abbr>) Management Board.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2016-08-11T13:23:19Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Chief Executive, UK Trade & Investment","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-01-12T15:09:51Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Nick Baird CMG CVO - Chief Executive, UK Trade & Investment